             was indicted for <rs id="t18270712-44-off248" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18270712-44-off248" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270712-44-off248" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18270712-44-cd249" type="crimeDate">4th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270712-44-off248 t18270712-44-cd249"></join>, 2 sovereigns, 12 shillings, and 4 sixpences, the monies of 
                     <persName id="t18270712-44-victim341" type="victimName">
                        Patrick 
                        Connolly
                     <interp inst="t18270712-44-victim341" type="surname" value="Connolly"></interp>
