                     <interp inst="t18270712-44-verdict252" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               GUILTY. Aged 21. Of stealing to the value of 39s. only
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Recommended to Mercy. - <rs id="t18270712-44-punish253" type="punishmentDescription">
